{
  "id": "RAW_96a3fd21",
  "title": "2026 开年关键词：Self-Distillation，大模型真正走向「持续学习」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651016237&idx=2&sn=a40e285b0b27d5abd99ff5f4ed1ae12d",
  "date": "2026-02-10 03:44:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d69cdbc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGvQCHNoyYKibd22sIhrDVJjkuhVVVFIWGibuY51swsuxAhcPELHN4BloA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span></span></p>\n  <p>开年最热的论文，竟都和Self-Distillation有关。</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.04259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503523662\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ed75af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicoCrHPEpT0tQiceNphESCa2eJTqstP8G0yqMTkeMFrOGue6kOyCKdTkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">机器之心编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49g9u\">2026 年刚拉开序幕，大模型（LLM）领域的研究者们似乎达成了一种默契。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491mi\">当你翻开最近 arXiv 上最受关注的几篇论文，会发现一个高频出现的词汇：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Self-Distillation</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49oqp\">近年来，基础模型取得了显著的成功，为语言、视觉、机器人等领域的 AI 应用提供了强大的支持。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49109\">但在真正落地、长期使用的过程中，研究者逐渐发现：如何让模型在不断吸收新知识的同时，不丢失已有的核心能力 —— 即「持续学习」，正成为制约大模型进化的关键瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls4914tu\">传统的强教师依赖范式因成本与数据依赖，难以适配高频的持续进化。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">Self-Distillation（自蒸馏）</span>&nbsp;随之成为破局点 ——&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">通过合理的上下文引导或反馈机制</span>，模型完全可以构建出一个比当前权重更聪明的临时自我，让模型在没有外部强教师的情况下实现内生增长。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49syx\">基于这一深刻洞察，由 MIT、ETH Zurich、Meta 及斯坦福等顶尖机构组成的紧密学术圈，在 2026 年 1 月密集发布了三项研究成果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67nd6d22g4\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ml67nd6z1jdn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.Self-Distillation Enables Continual Learning</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"236\" data-imgfileid=\"503531344\" data-ratio=\"0.1712962962962963\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 578px;height: 99px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1380\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92a144ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGXbDJ5kTyCGuOHpEQYibbbL310IY2PibHMZY4DLOic6bFOic4bIlNXe4H9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ml67vofiy6w\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"ml67voes13k3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">论文标题：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Self-Distillation Enables Continual Learning</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkz26h5phj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a href=\"https://www.alphaxiv.org/abs/2601.19897\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.alphaxiv.org/abs/2601.19897</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">代码链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkz26h5pe12\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a href=\"https://github.com/idanshen/Self-Distillation\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/idanshen/Self-Distillation</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49ieb\">在持续学习领域，传统的监督微调（SFT）常因<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;「灾难性遗忘」</span>&nbsp;备受诟病，它的副作用非常明显：当你教模型学会一套新的知识，它原有的代码能力或常识推理往往会发生断崖式下跌。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491p7v\">研究团队提出了一种自蒸馏微调（SDFT）方法，该方法能够直接从演示中实现基于策略的学习。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"334\" data-imgfileid=\"503531345\" data-ratio=\"0.47714285714285715\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" data-width=\"700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5e59051&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGE135hiavAnaJgGlBc7v57MN6n23Ag57XsUXWReuYhBnfl1T7icva0tibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:13px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml684f13q2g\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ml684f1qheo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">SDFT 机制概览</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49idw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">核心机制：</span>&nbsp;该方法假设预训练模型已具备强大的 ICL 潜力。在学习新知识时，首先构造包含少量专家演示（Few-shot）的上下文，诱导模型生成高质量的教师分布；随后要求模型在不带演示的情况下，通过自蒸馏去拟合这一分布。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls492362\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">技术突破：</span>&nbsp;该方法将持续学习转化为一个&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">策略内对齐问题</span>。由于训练信号源于模型自身的 ICL 状态，它能最大限度地保持模型原始的概率流分布，避免参数在微调过程中产生剧烈漂移，从而解决了监督微调（SFT）中常见的灾难性遗忘。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33611111111111114\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-width=\"1173\" data-height=\"394\" data-imgfileid=\"503531346\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed566123&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGeibBHz2xBGhyiaKEIGpoV1ibpeEcR9OSvk3iarB5jkXaPRcf2abGPGcAVA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49fmj\">在技能学习和知识获取任务中，SDFT 的表现一致优于 SFT：它不仅实现了更高的新任务准确率，还显著减少了灾难性遗忘。在顺序学习实验中，SDFT 使单一模型能够随时间累积多种技能而不会出现性能退化，证明了同策略蒸馏是从演示中实现持续学习的一种实用路径。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491dt2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2.Reinforcement Learning via Self-Distillation</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"390\" data-imgfileid=\"503531347\" data-ratio=\"0.3037037037037037\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1284\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f847525e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGickwQEvFopfbkVAXaJDjqWTxd9Zf02GPRXGGc1amqz13K0H3T0uu4rw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ml67vofiy6w\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"ml67voes13k3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">论文标题：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Reinforcement Learning via Self-Distillation</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkz26h5phj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2601.20802\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2601.20802</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">代码链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkz26h5pe12\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a href=\"https://github.com/lasgroup/SDPO\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/lasgroup/SDPO</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491f2n\">目前的强化学习（如 GRPO）通常只能拿到一个二值反馈，这在长程推理中会导致严重的「信用分配」问题。此外，在 GRPO 等算法中，如果模型在某组尝试中全军覆没（奖励均为 0），学习信号就会消失，导致模型进化停滞。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49l1d\">研究团队认为，问题的关键并不在于强化学习本身，而在于<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">常见的二值反馈信息密度极低</span>，无法为长逻辑链条提供精细的指导。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491gx9\">针对这一困境，研究团队提出了 SDPO（自蒸馏策略优化） 框架，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">旨在将环境中的 「富反馈」 转化为高效的学习信号</span>。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"446\" data-imgfileid=\"503531348\" data-ratio=\"0.33611111111111114\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1328\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e5ee4bb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGmEsDbKuK4bQtTicv6Puuc9pRcK55c0N5jfmWr5LMEZjkS8psLLObtIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:13px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491ndp\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">RLVR 与 RLRF 强化学习范式对比</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491as2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">核心机制：&nbsp;</span>SDPO 引入了 富反馈（Rich Feedback） 环境。当模型生成错误答案时，环境会返回具体的报错信息（如逻辑判读）。模型将这些报错信息重新注入上下文，作为一个 「自省教师」 来重新审视并校准之前的错误尝试。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491ur0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">技术突破：</span>&nbsp;该方法通过自蒸馏机制，将原本模糊的标量奖励转化为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Token 级的密集监督信号</span>。通过对比 「反馈后分布」 与 「初始分布」 的差异，SDPO 能精准定位导致失败的关键 Token，指引模型降低错误路径的概率，并提高修正后逻辑的置信度。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47129629629629627\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-width=\"1368\" data-height=\"645\" data-imgfileid=\"503531349\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0354fe76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGsScVMkuUZQrxlEhgic6kvHyKZjpndTkNzKa3wr2YofTNDicASdp0dyqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls4918h1\">在极难任务（左图）中，SDPO（绿线）展现了极高的采样效率，仅需约<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;1/3 的尝试次数（3× speedup）</span>即可达到其他算法的解发现率。而在整体训练维度上，它能以更少的样本量快速收敛，在 k=1000 时已能解决&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">70%</span>&nbsp;的困难任务，显著突破了传统算法的性能瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49s05\">在 LiveCodeBench 等竞赛级编程测试中，SDPO 展现了惊人的学习效率：它仅需传统 GRPO 算法<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;1/4 的生成样本量&nbsp;</span>即可达到同等精度。它证明了即便没有外部强教师，模型也能通过利用环境反馈进行深度自省，从而打破标量奖励带来的进化僵局。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491b5x\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3.Self-Distilled Reasoner:&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491b5x\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">On-Policy Self-Distillation for Large Language Models</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-width=\"1312\" data-height=\"280\" data-imgfileid=\"503531350\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b395c58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGrb3X9icbMkzrmn8q15XnvQfZU8TvhYcYicQIGrzO9wcBoMRIvibC2xqIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ml67vofiy6w\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"ml67voes13k3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">论文标题：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Self-Distilled Reasoner: On-Policy Self-Distillation for Large Language Models</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkz26h5phj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2601.18734\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2601.18734</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49xbo\">在复杂推理任务中，大模型往往面临<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">搜索空间过大</span>、<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">奖励信号稀疏</span>的问题。尽管强化学习能提升模型上限，但在没有外部 「强教师」 辅助的在线学习场景中，模型很难在短时间内找到通往正确答案的深层逻辑路径。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491v09\">研究团队提出了 OPSD（策略内自蒸馏） 框架，通过在同一模型内部构建 「信息不对称」 来引导自我进化。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"281\" data-imgfileid=\"503531351\" data-ratio=\"0.2744140625\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74d36a31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWGngay6icNrMntiaXX1HmyzTUsDxaLibEnDFDM76YWzibWbhU3oGEJuEjia6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:13px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls49159v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;OPSD 框架概览</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls4923yz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">核心机制：&nbsp;</span>该框架将模型配置为两种状态。教师策略在输入中包含 「特权信息」（如标准答案或经过验证的推理轨迹），能够产生高质量的 Token 概率分布；而学生策略则在不接触特权信息的情况下仅凭题目进行作答。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls4936q\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">技术突破：&nbsp;</span>OPSD 采用 策略内（On-Policy）采样，核心训练目标是最小化学生分布与教师分布之间的 KL 散度。这种设计强制模型在不借助外部参考的情况下，通过内生分布的对齐，学会如何从题目直接推导出具有逻辑深度的推理链路。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"395\" data-imgfileid=\"503531352\" data-ratio=\"0.23796296296296296\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1660\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24562a98&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibnuawEGIclTM0wnuLx1ZWG7P87rndRYXiaYzpUrOp4nDx8x24EW4kiarB6ZZwAhibNglAA7VVc0Jkqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\">在 MATH 和 GSM8K 等高难度推理基准测试中，OPSD 展现了极高的学习效率：它在 Token 利用率上比传统的 GRPO 算法高出&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">4-8 倍</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\">。实验证明，SFT 虽然能提供初始方向，但 OPSD 能够更进一步地挖掘模型内在的“推理潜力”，证明了通过特权信息诱导出的自我博弈，是实现推理能力飞跃的一条捷径。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls4951t\">这三篇论文核心逻辑高度一致：利用模型已有的内生能力，通过不同的上下文构造出 「信息差」，从而实现自驱动的闭环升级，Self-Distillation 正在成为大模型后训练阶段（Post-training）的标准配置。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"ml67ls491xi\">2026 年，也许我们不再需要教模型怎么变强，只需要给它一个「持续学习」的机会。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度解析了 2026 年大模型领域的核心趋势——自蒸馏（Self-Distillation），通过三项前沿研究展示了模型如何利用内生能力实现持续学习与推理进化的闭环。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度解析了 2026 年大模型领域的核心趋势——自蒸馏（Self-Distillation），通过三项前沿研究展示了模型如何利用内生能力实现持续学习与推理进化的闭环。",
  "summary": "文章聚焦于 2026 年初大模型研究的重大转向，即从依赖外部强教师转向利用“自蒸馏”技术实现内生增长。核心内容围绕 MIT、ETH Zurich、Meta 等机构的三项研究展开：首先是 SDFT 方法，通过上下文学习构造临时教师分布，解决了持续学习中的灾难性遗忘；其次是 SDPO 框架，利用环境提供的“富反馈”信息，将稀疏的二值奖励转化为 Token 级的密集监督信号，大幅提升强化学习效率；最后是 OPSD 框架，通过在模型内部构建“信息不对称”，利用特权信息引导学生策略学习深层推理逻辑。这些研究共同预示着大模型正走向自驱动的持续进化阶段。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "SDFT 利用上下文学习构造临时教师分布，有效解决了持续学习中的灾难性遗忘问题。",
      "explanation": "该方法通过 Few-shot 诱导模型生成高质量分布，再让模型在无演示情况下进行自蒸馏拟合。这种策略内对齐能最大限度保持原始概率流，避免微调导致的参数剧烈漂移和性能下跌。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SDPO 框架通过引入环境“富反馈”，将模糊的标量奖励转化为 Token 级的密集监督信号。",
      "explanation": "当模型出错时，将具体报错信息重新注入上下文作为“自省教师”。通过对比反馈前后分布差异，精准定位错误 Token，显著提升了长程推理任务中的采样效率和收敛速度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OPSD 框架通过在模型内部构建“信息不对称”，利用特权信息引导模型实现推理能力的自我进化。",
      "explanation": "教师策略接触标准答案等特权信息，学生策略则仅凭题目作答。通过最小化两者间的 KL 散度，强制模型在不借助外部参考的情况下，挖掘内在潜力并学会深层逻辑推理。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Self-Distillation（自蒸馏）随之成为破局点 —— 通过合理的上下文引导或反馈机制，模型完全可以构建出一个比当前权重更聪明的临时自我。",
    "该方法将持续学习转化为一个策略内对齐问题。由于训练信号源于模型自身的 ICL 状态，它能最大限度地保持模型原始的概率流分布。",
    "问题的关键并不在于强化学习本身，而在于常见的二值反馈信息密度极低，无法为长逻辑链条提供精细的指导。",
    "2026 年，也许我们不再需要教模型怎么变强，只需要给它一个‘持续学习’的机会。"
  ],
